==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Notodontian
<hw>No`to*don"tian</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>nw^ton</grk> the back + <grk>'odoy`s</grk>, <grk>'odo`ntos</grk> a
tooth.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Any one of several species of
bombycid moths belonging to <gen>Notodonta</gen>, <gen>Nerice</gen>, and
allied genera. The caterpillar of these moths has a hump, or spine, on
its back.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Notophthalmus</ent>⟦br⟧
